<section class="x51c-lab" aria-label="X51C AI 商品图决策工作台">
  <header class="lab-hero">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow">X51C CASE STUDY</span>
      <h2>AI 最后才出图，前面先做 5 次判断</h2>
      <p>
        这次我没有把产品图和一句 Prompt 直接丢给模型，而是先把商品事实、竞品表达、卖点优先级、图片计划和人工确认逐层固定下来。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="route-compare" aria-label="旧做法和新做法对比">
      <div class="route-row route-old">
        <span class="route-tag">旧做法</span>
        <div class="route-line">
          <span>商品资料</span><i>→</i><span>一句 Prompt</span><i>→</i><strong>AI 自己猜</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="route-row route-new">
        <span class="route-tag">现在</span>
        <div class="route-line route-line-new">
          <span>事实</span><i>→</i><span>分析</span><i>→</i><span>判断</span><i>→</i><span>确认</span><i>→</i><strong>出图</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="metric-strip" aria-label="X51C 工作流当前数据">
    <div><span>信息来源</span><strong>3 类</strong><small>商品资料 · 竞品 · 用户反馈</small></div>
    <div><span>决策中间件</span><strong>1 份</strong><small>商品图片生成计划.md</small></div>
    <div><span>规划图片</span><strong>16 张</strong><small>6 张主图 · 10 屏详情图</small></div>
    <div><span>已生成测试</span><strong>4 张</strong><small>3 张首图方向 · 1 张触控板图</small></div>
  </div>

  <section class="pipeline-panel">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <span class="eyebrow">DECISION PIPELINE</span>
      <h3>真正的生产线，是把“画什么”先决定清楚</h3>
      <p>每一站都要留下可检查的产出；上一站没有通过，下一站就不能自由发挥。</p>
    </div>

    <ol class="pipeline-rail">
      <li>
        <span class="stage-index">01</span>
        <div class="stage-copy">
          <small>FACT</small>
          <strong>核对商品事实</strong>
          <p>只接收已确认的参数、结构、接口、配件和真实产品图。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stage-output">产出：已确认 / 缺失 / 禁止推测</div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="stage-index">02</span>
        <div class="stage-copy">
          <small>MARKET</small>
          <strong>看竞品怎么表达</strong>
          <p>分析首图钩子、主图分工、详情页顺序和视觉机会点。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stage-output">产出：可借鉴点 / 不照搬点</div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="stage-index">03</span>
        <div class="stage-copy">
          <small>JUDGEMENT</small>
          <strong>给卖点排优先级</strong>
          <p>把卖点分成一级、二级、三级，决定什么先讲、什么后讲。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stage-output">产出：主图与详情页说服顺序</div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="stage-index">04</span>
        <div class="stage-copy">
          <small>PLAN</small>
          <strong>落盘整套图片计划</strong>
          <p>每张图写清目标、文案、构图、真实依据、禁止项和审核标准。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stage-output">产出：商品图片生成计划.md</div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="stage-index">05</span>
        <div class="stage-copy">
          <small>CONFIRM</small>
          <strong>运营确认方向</strong>
          <p>首图方向、最大卖点、视觉风格和表达边界先在计划阶段定稿。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stage-output">产出：可执行的最终计划</div>
      </li>
      <li class="stage-final">
        <span class="stage-index">06</span>
        <div class="stage-copy">
          <small>GENERATE</small>
          <strong>拆成单图任务再生成</strong>
          <p>真实产品图负责事实，单图任务负责目标，模型只负责完成画面。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stage-output">产出：测试图 → 人工审核 → 上线</div>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <div class="logic-grid">
    <section class="role-board">
      <div class="section-heading compact">
        <span class="eyebrow">BUSINESS ROLES</span>
        <h3>不是三个 Skill，而是三类业务判断</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="role-row">
        <span class="role-mark role-main">总控</span>
        <div>
          <strong>把所有信息合成最终图片方案</strong>
          <p>决定资料够不够、卖点怎么排、主图做什么、详情页怎么展开。</p>
        </div>
        <small>不能跳过计划和确认</small>
      </div>
      <div class="role-row">
        <span class="role-mark role-market">看市场</span>
        <div>
          <strong>研究竞品为什么这样表达</strong>
          <p>看点击钩子、图片分工、详情页节奏和没有讲清楚的机会点。</p>
        </div>
        <small>不能把竞品事实变成我方事实</small>
      </div>
      <div class="role-row">
        <span class="role-mark role-user">听用户</span>
        <div>
          <strong>把评价问题映射成图片动作</strong>
          <p>尺寸误解做尺寸图，套装误解做清单图；不适合图片解决的问题就不硬塞。</p>
        </div>
        <small>没有评价资料时直接跳过</small>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="boundary-gate">
      <div class="section-heading compact">
        <span class="eyebrow">FACT GATE</span>
        <h3>事实边界像一道闸门</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="gate-lane gate-pass">
        <span class="gate-status">已确认</span>
        <strong>可以进入图片计划</strong>
        <p>触控板 · 单蓝牙 · Type-C · 280mAh · 多系统支持</p>
      </div>
      <div class="gate-lane gate-wait">
        <span class="gate-status">待补充</span>
        <strong>缺了就暂停对应任务</strong>
        <p>尺寸重量 · 包装清单 · 部分标准角度 · SKU 颜色名称</p>
      </div>
      <div class="gate-lane gate-stop">
        <span class="gate-status">禁止推测</span>
        <strong>再好看也不能写进去</strong>
        <p>三模 · 机械键盘 · 背光 · 防水 · 未确认续航天数</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section class="trace-panel">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <span class="eyebrow">SINGLE IMAGE TRACE</span>
      <h3>X51C 主图 2：一张触控板卖点图是怎么被决定出来的</h3>
      <p>下面不是提示词拆解，而是一条从商品事实到最终执行的证据链。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="trace-layout">
      <div class="evidence-chain">
        <div class="evidence-node">
          <span>商品事实</span>
          <strong>X51C 带真实触控板</strong>
          <p>这是已确认结构，不是根据竞品猜出来的功能。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="evidence-node">
          <span>业务判断</span>
          <strong>解释“为什么选触控款”</strong>
          <p>重点不是炫技，而是减少输入时频繁抬手触屏。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="evidence-node">
          <span>图片计划</span>
          <strong>主图 2 只讲一个卖点</strong>
          <p>标题定为“带触控板 操作更顺手”，视觉焦点锁定触控区域。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="evidence-node">
          <span>单图任务</span>
          <strong>45° 产品视角 + 局部放大</strong>
          <p>允许加手指示意；禁止宣称替代鼠标、专业绘图或高级手势。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="execution-console">
        <div class="console-head">
          <span>STRUCTURE CONTROL</span>
          <strong>真实图片分工，而不是让 AI 自己补结构</strong>
        </div>

        <div class="reference-pair">
          <div>
            <span>角度参考</span>
            <strong>IMG_3292.jpg</strong>
            <small>提供触控板可见的 45° 主视角</small>
          </div>
          <i>+</i>
          <div>
            <span>结构校准</span>
            <strong>IMG_3281.jpg</strong>
            <small>锁定键位、触控板位置和产品比例</small>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="keyboard-schematic" aria-label="X51C 键盘结构示意">
          <div class="keys" aria-hidden="true">
            <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
            <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
            <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
            <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="touchpad">
            <small>真实触控板区域</small>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="generation-path">
          <span>两张实拍图</span><i>→</i><span>单图任务</span><i>→</i><span>GPT Image 2</span><i>→</i><strong>X51C-main-02-touchpad-v1.png</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="progress-panel">
    <div class="progress-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow">CURRENT STATUS</span>
      <h3>这套流程已经跑到“单图测试”，还没有假装成完整闭环</h3>
      <p>我更愿意把当前做到哪里写清楚，而不是把一个还在验证中的流程包装成成熟系统。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="progress-track" aria-label="X51C 工作流当前进度">
      <div class="progress-item done"><span>01</span><strong>商品资料整理</strong><small>完成</small></div>
      <div class="progress-item done"><span>02</span><strong>竞品与卖点分析</strong><small>完成</small></div>
      <div class="progress-item done"><span>03</span><strong>图片计划定稿</strong><small>完成</small></div>
      <div class="progress-item current"><span>04</span><strong>单图拆解与测试生成</strong><small>已跑到这里</small></div>
      <div class="progress-item"><span>05</span><strong>整套主图 / 详情图</strong><small>待继续</small></div>
      <div class="progress-item"><span>06</span><strong>人工审核与上线</strong><small>待验证</small></div>
      <div class="progress-item"><span>07</span><strong>点击率 / 转化率迭代</strong><small>尚未闭环</small></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="lab-verdict">
    <span>最终判断</span>
    <strong>AI 图片生成只是最后一个执行节点。真正决定结果的，是前面的事实、判断、计划和确认。</strong>
  </footer>
</section>

